(foo : Π X : C, X ⟶ X)
(bar : ∀ {X Y : C} (f : X ⟶ Y), foo X ≫ f = f ≫ foo Y)

reassoc_axiom some_class.bar
```

The above will produce:

```lean
lemma some_class.bar_assoc {Z : C} (g : Y ⟶ Z) :
  foo X ≫ f ≫ g = f ≫ foo Y ≫ g := ...
